name: THE SACRED CYCLOP
description:
We have detected in an ancient forgotten crater, located in the Tropic of Cancer, at a latitude of 23º 26 ′ 14 ″ north of the equator, the surprising exit of an entity that remained hidden inside the planet Earth.

Everything seems to indicate that its emergence is connected with the arrival of other beings of the same nature.

We will continue looking for signs of communication.
